  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The 901st Tactical Wing, better known as Vagabond Squadron, flies Valkyrie assault craft in the dirty close-support war that more glamorous pilots prefer to mock. Sent to Kanai Tertius as Ork air power rises over a collapsing Imperial front, the squadron has to keep troops moving, extractions open, and a novice aviator alive under pressure. Robbie MacNiven turns the air war into a cockpit-level ensemble piece: hot engines, chain-of-command friction, and transport pilots proving that survival often depends on the craft everyone else overlooks.",
